thread.title: Jamie Williams

author: Jamie Williams
title: Jamie Williams
text:
I have had a very bad experience using airtasker and after escalating the issue to airtasker no one has called me.
One of you airtaskers has taken my house keys for over 1 week after lending her a set to complete a 1 day job. In this circumstance airtasker should have got involved and spoke with the tradie. Another issue is that I don't have her direct phone number.
I still don't have my set of keys back and still no call from airtasker
